Package ohos.data.search.model

Class IndexData

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.search.model.IndexData
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Schema

    public class IndexData
extends Object
    Represents a container that stores index data.

    The index data is in key-value pair format. Neither the key nor value can be null. Currently, five data types are supported: string, integer, long, double, and float.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_SEARCH
